{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was starting to tell you before, but we never sort of got to any conclusion there, that my very early reaction, right, against the-- against the restrictive measures which came into force and the-- and the adverse propaganda which always accompanied that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the reaction I got out of that that I started to query myself, right?",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I almost started to give the benefit of the doubt to them, right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that, as I said earlier, it didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I realized that they are wrong, and we are right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During this time, I sought the company of non-Jewish friends, which I had, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] look, I was in a-- in a tremendous quandary at that time, I-- if I remember well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, because I-- being a Hungarian-- I felt that I belonged to-- there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they accepted me because they needed me to recite their poems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They needed me to kick their goals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it, it was no problem to, to be with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I liked that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I liked that, the Jewish boy being there, accepted and, and, and appreciated, right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was, I think, at the expense of my, my, my Jewish connections, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, I, I never denied that I was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always went to the synagogue, and I did everything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in my social life, perhaps, I had this conscious orientation for a year, a couple of years or so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As, however, things deteriorated, I-- and I, I, I went through this metamorphosis-- I got my back up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- and the reaction set in by saying, to hell with you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will keep-- I will keep reciting your poems, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
